div1.p: UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON NORTHERN DIVISION.
In the Matter of the Unlawful Detention of Seventy-six Hindoo Aliens. : : : :

On oral motion of the respondent herein, petitioners agreeing hereto, it is hereby ordered that the respondent may file in connection with his return the original files of the proceedings before the Immigration Bureau in lieu of the copies hereto- fore filed and may withdraw said copies.
IN THE DISTRICT COURT OF THE UNITED STATES FOR THE WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON
IN THE MATTER OF THE UNLAWFUL DETENTION OF SEVENTY-SIX HINDOO ALIENS.
FILED IN THE U.S. District Court, Western Dist. of Washington. SEP 9 1913 FRANK L. CROSBY, Clerk, By Emy Deputy
